label("$B$", pB, SE);
label("$C$", pC, NW);
label("$D$", pD, NE);
label("$E$", pE, 3 * N);
label("$6$", pA--pB, S);
label("$10$", pA--pC, W);
label("$6$", pB--pD, E);
draw(rightanglemark(pB,pA,pC,12));
draw(rightanglemark(pD,pB,pA,12));
[/asy] What is the area of $\triangle ACE$?

